ed by Bush – Trump’s tax reform bill will have nowhere near the effect on revenue that Reagan’s did.", "url": "https://www.cnn.com/2017/12/15/politics/is-trumps-bill-largest-tax-cut-in-history-no/index.html"}], "pred_label": "Refuted", "llm_output": "<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

