ps://www.usatoday.com/story/opinion/2020/07/23/racism-eugenics-margaret-sanger-deserves-no-honors-column/5480192002/"}, {"question": "Did Margaret Sanger's views on eugenics align with her goals when founding Planned Parenthood?", "answer": "Charges that Sanger's motives for promoting birth control were eugenic are not supported. In part of her most important work, "Pivot of Civilization," Sanger's dissent from eugenics was made clear.", "url": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/3884362/"}, {"question": "What aspects of Margaret Sanger's life and work are being referred to as racist?", "answer": ""Margaret Sanger's concerns and advocacy for reproductive health have been clearly documented, but so too has her racist legacy.", "url": "https://www.newsweek.com/margaret-sanger-controversial-eugenics-beliefs-planned-parenthood-1519695"}], "pred_label": "Supported", "llm_output": "<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

