her to vote in favor of invading Iraq in 2002, he took President George W. Bush at his word and was led astray.", "url": "https://www.vox.com/policy-and-politics/2019/10/15/20849072/joe-biden-iraq-history-democrats-election-2020"}], "pred_label": "Supported", "llm_output": "<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

