{"claim_id": 56, "claim": "Democratic Arizona Superintendent of Public Instruction Kathy Hoffman is “pushing” for sex education that would teach kindergartners about masturbation and sexual positions.", "evidence": [{"question": "Is Kathy Hoffman pushing to teach kindergartners about masturbation and sexual positions in sex education?", "answer": "In an Arizona State Board of Education meeting in June, Hoffman proposed removing language from state sex education guidelines that forbids "the teaching of abnormal, deviate, or unusual sexual acts and practices."", "url": "https://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-education/2020/01/09/arizona-legislature-could-outlaw-discussion-school-sex-education-seventh-grade-homosexuality-sb-1082/2849132001/"}, {"question": "Does Democratic Arizona Superintendent of Public Instruction Kathy Hoffman support changing state sex-ed guidelines in public schools?", "answer": "Bowers, a Republican, also called Democratic State Superintendent Kathy Hoffman a "radical" over her support for changing state sex-ed guidelines to promote scientifically accurate instruction in public schools, according to footage of his remarks recorded by the anti-migrant group Patriot Movement AZ.", "url": "https://www.phoenixnewtimes.com/news/planned-parenthood-arizona-speaker-rusty-bowers-abortions-stds-11359548"}, {"question": "Does Arizona law allow schools to develop sex education curricula for students of all ages, including kindergartners?", "answer": "Arizona law currently allows schools to develop “age-appropriate” sex ed curriculum for students of all ages, and parents must opt-in to the classes.", "url": "https://www.azmirror.com/2020/01/08/arizona-sex-ed-banned-7th-grade-gop-proposal/"}, {"question": "Does the evidence contradict the claim that Kathy Hoffman is pushing for sex education that would teach kindergartners about masturbation and sexual positions?", "answer": "Arizona students wouldn’t be allowed to take sexual education classes until the seventh grade, and parents could sue school districts if that class included discussions about homosexuality or failed to primarily focus on abstinence under a plan introduced Wednesday by the conservative head of the Arizona Senate’s Education Committee.", "url": "https://www.azmirror.com/2020/01/08/arizona-sex-ed-banned-7th-grade-gop-proposal/"}, {"question": "Does the sex education policy in Arizona emphasize abstinence-only education?", "answer": "Arizona's rules require that educators stress abstinence-only education. The rules do not mandate that schools teach about contraception or that sex education be medically accurate.", "url": "https://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-education/2020/01/09/arizona-legislature-could-outlaw-discussion-school-sex-education-seventh-grade-homosexuality-sb-1082/2849132001/"}, {"question": "Can parents in Arizona opt their children out of sex education classes if they disagree with the content taught?", "answer": "Sex education is optional in Arizona — parents may opt their children in or out of the lessons. Districts and charter schools set sex education curricula.", "url": "https://eu.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-education/2019/06/24/state-board-education-leaves-sex-ed-unchanged-after-intense-meeting/1549659001/"}, {"question": "Does Arizona require sex education to be taught in schools?", "answer": "Schools in Arizona do not have to teach sex education. It is not among the 24 states that require sex education, according to the National Conference of State Legislators.", "url": "https://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-education/2020/01/09/arizona-legislature-could-outlaw-discussion-school-sex-education-seventh-grade-homosexuality-sb-1082/2849132001/"}, {"question": "Does the current sex education policy in Arizona allow for the teaching of age-appropriate topics in earlier grades?", "answer": "- Prohibits sex-ed instruction until seventh grade, with an exception for health instruction including "age-appropriate" instruction on hormonal changes, like menstruation.", "url": "https://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-education/2020/01/09/arizona-legislature-could-outlaw-discussion-school-sex-education-seventh-grade-homosexuality-sb-1082/2849132001/"}, {"question": "Is Arizona Superintendent of Public Instruction Kathy Hoffman actively advocating for the implementation of a specific sex education bill in Arizona schools?", "answer": "Arizona Superintendent of Public Instruction Kathy Hoffman, an advocate for LGBTQ rights in schools, said the Arizona Department of Education was still researching the possible ramifications of the bill.", "url": "https://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-education/2020/01/09/arizona-legislature-could-outlaw-discussion-school-sex-education-seventh-grade-homosexuality-sb-1082/2849132001/"}, {"question": "Is the proposed sex education bill by Arizona Superintendent of Public Instruction Kathy Hoffman intended to increase parent involvement in the development of sex education instruction?", "answer": "The bill, she told The Republic, is meant to stoke parent involvement as schools develop sex education instruction, imposing requirements for schools changing or creating a new curriculum.", "url": "https://www.azcentral.com/story/news/local/arizona-education/2020/01/09/arizona-legislature-could-outlaw-discussion-school-sex-education-seventh-grade-homosexuality-sb-1082/2849132001/"}], "pred_label": "Refuted", "llm_output": "<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

