ildren should not be forced to recite the pledge. In 1954, the pledge underwent its final change -- and a controversial one at that -- when the phrase "under God" was added.", "url": "https://www.wral.com/story/news/local/story/115966/"}], "pred_label": "Refuted", "llm_output": "<|start_header_id|>assistant<|end_header_id|>

